documentation:
Request model for editing text file contents.

Example:
{
    "files": [
        {
            "path": "/path/to/file",
            "hash": "abc123...",
            "patches": [
                {
                    "line_start": 1,  # default: 1 (top of file)
                    "line_end": null,  # default: null (end of file)
                    "contents": "new content"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
